Base Rate: Take a private boat trip around the stunning Gili Islands. Snorkel through vibrant coral reefs, swim with sea turtles, and visit the famous underwater statues. A GoPro is provided to capture all the magic and make memories you'll never forget.

Take a private boat trip around the stunning Gili Islands. Snorkel through vibrant coral reefs, swim with sea turtles, and visit the famous underwater statues. A GoPro is provided to capture all the magic and make memories you'll never forget.
Experience the breathtaking sunset from a private boat, complete with drinks and snacks.
Pamper yourself with a rejuvenating massage in the comfort of your private villa.
Order our romantic floating breakfast and enjoy it in your private pool.
Enjoy some adult time with our nanny service.
Enjoy some french Champagne in your pool after your arrival.
Enjoy a bottle of Cava in your pool or on your terrasse after your arrival.
Enjoy our selection of cocktails in your villa or at the bar.
Let us offer you your transfer from Bali.
Enjoy our 5 course voyage across the spice island from our restaurant.
Enjoy our 7 course voyage across the spice island from our restaurant.
